    outcome: "The **Entente** won. **Germany**, **Austria-Hungary**, the **Ottoman Empire**, and the **Russian Empire** all collapsed. The **Treaty of Versailles** blamed Germany for everything, took its colonies, shrunk its army, and handed it a **reparations** bill so large it destabilized the entire global economy. The **League of Nations** was created to prevent future wars. It did not prevent future wars. The 'war to end all wars' set up the conditions for an even bigger one twenty years later. Humanity speedran the worst possible lesson-learning curve.",
