      result: "Inconclusive; Kashmir divided along ceasefire line; UN plebiscite promised (never held); three more wars to follow",
      belligerents: "India vs Pakistan & tribal lashkars",
      strength: "~30,000 Indian vs ~30,000–50,000 Pakistani/tribal",
